{
  "video_id": "jM9Q3xP2iBo",
  "title": "Do kids think of sperm donors as family? | Veerle Provoost",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12842.0,
      "end_time": 15400.0,
      "text": "What is a parent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15999.0,
      "end_time": 17606.0,
      "text": "What is a parent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19430.0,
      "end_time": 21151.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not an easy question."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21630.0,
      "end_time": 24300.0,
      "text": "Today we have adoption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24280.0,
      "end_time": 25604.0,
      "text": "stepfamilies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25628.0,
      "end_time": 27850.0,
      "text": "surrogate mothers."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27846.0,
      "end_time": 30259.0,
      "text": "Many parents face tough questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31151.0,
      "end_time": 32680.0,
      "text": "and tough decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33888.0,
      "end_time": 37141.0,
      "text": "Shall we tell our child about the sperm donation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39322.0,
      "end_time": 40697.0,
      "text": "If so, when?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41176.0,
      "end_time": 42776.0,
      "text": "What words to use?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43522.0,
      "end_time": 49382.0,
      "text": "Sperm donors are often referred to as \"biological fathers,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49407.0,
      "end_time": 52406.0,
      "text": "but should we really be using the word \"father?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53843.0,
      "end_time": 56248.0,
      "text": "As a philosopher and social scientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56272.0,
      "end_time": 60494.0,
      "text": "I have been studying these questions about the concept of parenthood."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61880.0,
      "end_time": 64116.0,
      "text": "But today, I will talk to you about what I learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64140.0,
      "end_time": 66280.0,
      "text": "from talking to parents and children."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67377.0,
      "end_time": 71731.0,
      "text": "I will show you that they know what matters most in a family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71755.0,
      "end_time": 74286.0,
      "text": "even though their family looks a little different."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75133.0,
      "end_time": 80134.0,
      "text": "I will show you their creative ways of dealing with tough questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 81287.0,
      "end_time": 85370.0,
      "text": "But I will also show you the parents&#39; uncertainties."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 87284.0,
      "end_time": 88815.0,
      "text": "We interviewed couples"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88839.0,
      "end_time": 92241.0,
      "text": "who received fertility treatment at Ghent University Hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 93750.0,
      "end_time": 94814.0,
      "text": "using sperm from a donor."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 95183.0,
      "end_time": 96750.0,
      "text": "In this treatment timeline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 96774.0,
      "end_time": 100660.0,
      "text": "you can see two points at which we conducted interviews."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100994.0,
      "end_time": 103426.0,
      "text": "We included heterosexual couples,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 104550.0,
      "end_time": 107927.0,
      "text": "where the man for some reason did not have good-quality sperm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 108435.0,
      "end_time": 113553.0,
      "text": "and lesbian couples who obviously needed to find sperm elsewhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 114996.0,
      "end_time": 117193.0,
      "text": "We also included children."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 118878.0,
      "end_time": 120361.0,
      "text": "I wanted to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 120385.0,
      "end_time": 125180.0,
      "text": "how those children define concepts like parenthood and family."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 126150.0,
      "end_time": 128951.0,
      "text": "In fact, that is what I asked them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 130258.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131697.0,
      "text": "only not in that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 133437.0,
      "end_time": 136960.0,
      "text": "I drew an apple tree instead."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 137560.0,
      "end_time": 140403.0,
      "text": "This way, I could ask abstract, philosophical questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 140427.0,
      "end_time": 143700.0,
      "text": "in a way that did not make them run off."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 145332.0,
      "end_time": 146983.0,
      "text": "So as you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 147800.0,
      "end_time": 148550.0,
      "text": "the apple tree is empty."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 149630.0,
      "end_time": 152243.0,
      "text": "And that illustrates my research approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 152659.0,
      "end_time": 154941.0,
      "text": "By designing techniques like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 154966.0,
      "end_time": 159739.0,
      "text": "I can bring as little meaning and content as possible to the interview,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 160533.0,
      "end_time": 162551.0,
      "text": "because I want to hear that from them."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 164362.0,
      "end_time": 165694.0,
      "text": "I asked them:"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 166738.0,
      "end_time": 169828.0,
      "text": "What would your family look like if it were an apple tree?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 170739.0,
      "end_time": 174489.0,
      "text": "And they could take a paper apple for everyone who, in their view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 174513.0,
      "end_time": 176120.0,
      "text": "was a member of the family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 176144.0,
      "end_time": 179318.0,
      "text": "write a name on it and hang it wherever they wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 179342.0,
      "end_time": 180912.0,
      "text": "And I would ask questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 182153.0,
      "end_time": 185278.0,
      "text": "Most children started with a parent or a sibling."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 185806.0,
      "end_time": 187970.0,
      "text": "One started with \"Boxer,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 188667.0,
      "end_time": 191175.0,
      "text": "the dead dog of his grandparents."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 191830.0,
      "end_time": 195688.0,
      "text": "At this point, none of the children started mentioning the donor."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 196465.0,
      "end_time": 200803.0,
      "text": "So, I asked them about their birth story."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 201161.0,
      "end_time": 203183.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Before you were born,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 203207.0,
      "end_time": 205570.0,
      "text": "it was just your mom and dad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 205594.0,
      "end_time": 206872.0,
      "text": "or mom and mommy."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 207421.0,
      "end_time": 210477.0,
      "text": "Can you tell me how you came into the family?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 211282.0,
      "end_time": 212721.0,
      "text": "And they explained."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 213602.0,
      "end_time": 214808.0,
      "text": "One said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 215691.0,
      "end_time": 218164.0,
      "text": "\"My parents did not have good seeds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 218865.0,
      "end_time": 222887.0,
      "text": "but there are friendly men out there who have spare seeds."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 223386.0,
      "end_time": 225136.0,
      "text": "They bring them to the hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 225160.0,
      "end_time": 227374.0,
      "text": "and they put them in a big jar."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 228249.0,
      "end_time": 229486.0,
      "text": "My mommy went there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 229510.0,
      "end_time": 232810.0,
      "text": "and she took two from the jar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 232786.0,
      "end_time": 234924.0,
      "text": "one for me and one for my sister."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 235725.0,
      "end_time": 237774.0,
      "text": "She put the seeds in her belly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 238161.0,
      "end_time": 239353.0,
      "text": "somehow --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 240236.0,
      "end_time": 242542.0,
      "text": "and her belly grew really big,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 242567.0,
      "end_time": 243819.0,
      "text": "and there I was.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 245289.0,
      "end_time": 246439.0,
      "text": "Hmm."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 248123.0,
      "end_time": 252191.0,
      "text": "So only when they started mentioning the donor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 252215.0,
      "end_time": 255440.0,
      "text": "I asked questions about him, using their own words."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 255926.0,
      "end_time": 257325.0,
      "text": "I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 257349.0,
      "end_time": 261815.0,
      "text": "\"If this would be an apple for the friendly man with the seeds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 261839.0,
      "end_time": 263172.0,
      "text": "what would you do with it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 264690.0,
      "end_time": 266427.0,
      "text": "And one boy was thinking out loud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 266451.0,
      "end_time": 267819.0,
      "text": "holding the apple."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 267843.0,
      "end_time": 269880.0,
      "text": "And he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 269890.0,
      "end_time": 272584.0,
      "text": "\"I won&#39;t put this one up there with the others."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 273239.0,
      "end_time": 275131.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s not part of my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 276191.0,
      "end_time": 278385.0,
      "text": "But I will not put him on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 278409.0,
      "end_time": 280319.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s too cold and too hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 281240.0,
      "end_time": 283325.0,
      "text": "I think he should be in the trunk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 284207.0,
      "end_time": 286550.0,
      "text": "because he made my family possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 287264.0,
      "end_time": 289218.0,
      "text": "If he would not have done this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 289242.0,
      "end_time": 293200.0,
      "text": "that would really be sad because my family would not be here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 293224.0,
      "end_time": 294820.0,
      "text": "and I would not be here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 297845.0,
      "end_time": 301373.0,
      "text": "So also, parents constructed family tales --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 301397.0,
      "end_time": 303154.0,
      "text": "tales to tell their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 304660.0,
      "end_time": 307787.0,
      "text": "One couple explained their insemination"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 307811.0,
      "end_time": 310334.0,
      "text": "by taking their children to a farm"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 311291.0,
      "end_time": 313852.0,
      "text": "to watch a vet inseminate cows."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 315656.0,
      "end_time": 317270.0,
      "text": "And why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 317510.0,
      "end_time": 319491.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s their way of explaining;"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 319515.0,
      "end_time": 322541.0,
      "text": "their do-it-yourself with family narratives."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 322981.0,
      "end_time": 324161.0,
      "text": "DIY."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 324533.0,
      "end_time": 326901.0,
      "text": "And we had another couple who made books --"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 326925.0,
      "end_time": 328380.0,
      "text": "a book for each child."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 328752.0,
      "end_time": 330274.0,
      "text": "They were really works of art"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 330298.0,
      "end_time": 333774.0,
      "text": "containing their thoughts and feelings throughout the treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 334192.0,
      "end_time": 336806.0,
      "text": "They even had the hospital parking tickets in there."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 337553.0,
      "end_time": 339174.0,
      "text": "So it is DIY:"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 339198.0,
      "end_time": 341580.0,
      "text": "finding ways, words and images"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 341604.0,
      "end_time": 344354.0,
      "text": "to tell your family story to your child."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 345717.0,
      "end_time": 348532.0,
      "text": "And these stories were highly diverse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 348940.0,
      "end_time": 351876.0,
      "text": "but they all had one thing in common:"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 353913.0,
      "end_time": 357134.0,
      "text": "it was a tale of longing for a child"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 357885.0,
      "end_time": 359563.0,
      "text": "and a quest for that child."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 360370.0,
      "end_time": 365437.0,
      "text": "It was about how special and how deeply loved their child was."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 367142.0,
      "end_time": 371790.0,
      "text": "And research so far shows that these children are doing fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 371814.0,
      "end_time": 374408.0,
      "text": "They do not have more problems than other kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 374854.0,
      "end_time": 379275.0,
      "text": "Yet, these parents also wanted to justify their decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 379299.0,
      "end_time": 380960.0,
      "text": "through the tales they tell."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 381505.0,
      "end_time": 384639.0,
      "text": "They hoped that their children would understand their reasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 384663.0,
      "end_time": 386498.0,
      "text": "for making the family in this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 387865.0,
      "end_time": 391819.0,
      "text": "Underlying was a fear that their children might disapprove"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 391843.0,
      "end_time": 394850.0,
      "text": "and would reject the non-genetic parent."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 394511.0,
      "end_time": 397131.0,
      "text": "And that fear is understandable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 397155.0,
      "end_time": 400195.0,
      "text": "because we live in a very heteronormative"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 400220.0,
      "end_time": 401958.0,
      "text": "and geneticized society --"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 402438.0,
      "end_time": 403930.0,
      "text": "a world that still believes"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 403954.0,
      "end_time": 408106.0,
      "text": "that true families consist of one mom, one dad"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 408130.0,
      "end_time": 410467.0,
      "text": "and their genetically related children."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 411738.0,
      "end_time": 412893.0,
      "text": "Well."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 414165.0,
      "end_time": 417266.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you about a teenage boy."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 417290.0,
      "end_time": 420590.0,
      "text": "He was donor-conceived but not part of our study."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 420658.0,
      "end_time": 423276.0,
      "text": "One day, he had an argument with his father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 423300.0,
      "end_time": 424592.0,
      "text": "and he yelled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 425305.0,
      "end_time": 427402.0,
      "text": "\"You&#39;re telling me what to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 427426.0,
      "end_time": 429306.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not even my father!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 431601.0,
      "end_time": 434983.0,
      "text": "That was exactly what the parents in our study feared."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 435984.0,
      "end_time": 439212.0,
      "text": "Now, the boy soon felt sorry, and they made up."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 439629.0,
      "end_time": 443400.0,
      "text": "But it is the reaction of his father that is most interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 444169.0,
      "end_time": 445342.0,
      "text": "He said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 445772.0,
      "end_time": 451134.0,
      "text": "\"This outburst had nothing to do with the lack of a genetic link."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 451765.0,
      "end_time": 454642.0,
      "text": "It was about puberty --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 455500.0,
      "end_time": 456445.0,
      "text": "being difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 456470.0,
      "end_time": 458233.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s what they do at that age."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 458792.0,
      "end_time": 460660.0,
      "text": "It will pass.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 461462.0,
      "end_time": 463318.0,
      "text": "What this man shows us"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 463342.0,
      "end_time": 465930.0,
      "text": "is that when something goes wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 466564.0,
      "end_time": 468165.0,
      "text": "we should not immediately think"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 468189.0,
      "end_time": 470596.0,
      "text": "it is because the family is a little different."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 471330.0,
      "end_time": 474416.0,
      "text": "These things happen in all families."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 475936.0,
      "end_time": 477426.0,
      "text": "And every now and then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 477818.0,
      "end_time": 479495.0,
      "text": "all parents may wonder:"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 480412.0,
      "end_time": 482441.0,
      "text": "Am I a good enough parent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 483164.0,
      "end_time": 484488.0,
      "text": "These parents, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 485990.0,
      "end_time": 489192.0,
      "text": "They, above all, wanted to do what&#39;s best for their child."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 489748.0,
      "end_time": 491643.0,
      "text": "But they also sometimes wondered:"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 492340.0,
      "end_time": 493810.0,
      "text": "Am I a real parent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 494288.0,
      "end_time": 498257.0,
      "text": "And their uncertainties were present long before they even were parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 498281.0,
      "end_time": 499713.0,
      "text": "At the start of treatment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 499737.0,
      "end_time": 501452.0,
      "text": "when they first saw the counselor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 502146.0,
      "end_time": 504841.0,
      "text": "they paid close attention to the counselor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 504865.0,
      "end_time": 506872.0,
      "text": "because they wanted to do it right."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 507853.0,
      "end_time": 509331.0,
      "text": "Even 10 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 510530.0,
      "end_time": 512672.0,
      "text": "they still remember the advice they were given."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 516981.0,
      "end_time": 519881.0,
      "text": "So when they thought about the counselor"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 520854.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522653.00000000006,
      "text": "and the advice they were given,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 522677.0,
      "end_time": 523840.0,
      "text": "we discussed that."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 523864.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527428.0,
      "text": "And we saw one lesbian couple who said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 528627.0,
      "end_time": 530231.0,
      "text": "\"When our son asks us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 530255.0,
      "end_time": 532304.0,
      "text": "&#39;Do I have a dad?&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 533482.0,
      "end_time": 536294.0,
      "text": "we will say &#39;No, you do not have a dad.&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 536839.0,
      "end_time": 539907.0,
      "text": "But we will say nothing more, not unless he asks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 540287.0,
      "end_time": 542315.0,
      "text": "because he might not be ready for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 542339.0,
      "end_time": 543839.0,
      "text": "The counselor said so.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 545350.0,
      "end_time": 546520.0,
      "text": "Well."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 547910.0,
      "end_time": 548993.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know; that&#39;s quite different"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 549170.0,
      "end_time": 551710.0,
      "text": "from how we respond to children&#39;s questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 552473.0,
      "end_time": 555274.0,
      "text": "Like, \"Milk -- is that made in a factory?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 555783.0,
      "end_time": 558945.0,
      "text": "We will say, \"No, it comes from cows,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 558969.0,
      "end_time": 560725.0,
      "text": "and we will talk about the farmer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 560749.0,
      "end_time": 562972.0,
      "text": "and the way the milk ends up in the shop."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 563806.0,
      "end_time": 565353.0,
      "text": "We will not say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 566102.0,
      "end_time": 569709.0,
      "text": "\"No, milk is not made in a factory.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 572420.0,
      "end_time": 574472.0,
      "text": "So something strange happened here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 574496.0,
      "end_time": 576853.0,
      "text": "and of course these children noticed that."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 577571.0,
      "end_time": 578856.0,
      "text": "One boy said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 579445.0,
      "end_time": 581837.0,
      "text": "\"I asked my parents loads of questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 581861.0,
      "end_time": 583670.0,
      "text": "but they acted really weird."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 584788.0,
      "end_time": 588732.0,
      "text": "So, you know, I have a friend at school, and she&#39;s made in the same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 589241.0,
      "end_time": 592241.0,
      "text": "When I have a question, I just go and ask her.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 593760.0,
      "end_time": 594968.0,
      "text": "Clever guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 595630.0,
      "end_time": 596927.0,
      "text": "Problem solved."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 597765.0,
      "end_time": 600348.0,
      "text": "But his parents did not notice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 600875.0,
      "end_time": 603457.0,
      "text": "and it certainly was not what they had in mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 603481.0,
      "end_time": 605415.0,
      "text": "nor what the counselor had in mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 605439.0,
      "end_time": 610636.0,
      "text": "when they were saying how important it is to be an open-communication family."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 612462.0,
      "end_time": 614716.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the strange thing about advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 614740.0,
      "end_time": 618360.0,
      "text": "When we offer people pills, we gather evidence first."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 618536.0,
      "end_time": 619791.0,
      "text": "We do tests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 619816.0,
      "end_time": 621117.0,
      "text": "we do follow-up studies."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 621141.0,
      "end_time": 625680.0,
      "text": "We want to know, and rightly so, what this pill is doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 625920.0,
      "end_time": 627588.0,
      "text": "and how it affects people&#39;s lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 628350.0,
      "end_time": 629356.0,
      "text": "And advice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 630748.0,
      "end_time": 632594.0,
      "text": "It is not enough for advice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 632618.0,
      "end_time": 637441.0,
      "text": "or for professionals to give advice that is theoretically sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 637465.0,
      "end_time": 638766.0,
      "text": "or well-meant."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 639447.0,
      "end_time": 642828.0,
      "text": "It should be advice that there is evidence for --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 642852.0,
      "end_time": 646752.0,
      "text": "evidence that it actually improves patients&#39; lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 648174.0,
      "end_time": 652737.0,
      "text": "So the philosopher in me would now like to offer you a paradox:"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 654308.0,
      "end_time": 658391.0,
      "text": "I advise you to stop following advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 659897.0,
      "end_time": 661289.0,
      "text": "But, yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 662221.0,
      "end_time": 665138.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 666591.0,
      "end_time": 669154.0,
      "text": "I will not end here with what went wrong;"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 669178.0,
      "end_time": 673414.0,
      "text": "I would not be doing justice to the warmth we found in those families."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 674931.0,
      "end_time": 677561.0,
      "text": "Remember the books and the trip to the farmer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 677585.0,
      "end_time": 681199.0,
      "text": "When parents do things that work for them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 681572.0,
      "end_time": 683145.0,
      "text": "they do brilliant things."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 684391.0,
      "end_time": 688340.0,
      "text": "What I want you to remember as members of families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 688580.0,
      "end_time": 690549.0,
      "text": "in no matter what form or shape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 690930.0,
      "end_time": 696276.0,
      "text": "is that what families need are warm relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 697409.0,
      "end_time": 700870.0,
      "text": "And we do not need to be professionals to create those."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 701644.0,
      "end_time": 703946.0,
      "text": "Most of us do just fine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 704986.0,
      "end_time": 706694.0,
      "text": "although it may be hard work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 707380.0,
      "end_time": 709908.0,
      "text": "and from time to time, we can do with some advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 711209.0,
      "end_time": 712479.0,
      "text": "In that case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 712504.0,
      "end_time": 714527.0,
      "text": "bear in mind three things."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 715760.0,
      "end_time": 719470.0,
      "text": "Work with advice that works for your family."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 720800.0,
      "end_time": 725486.0,
      "text": "Remember -- you&#39;re the expert, because you live your family life."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 726681.0,
      "end_time": 727965.0,
      "text": "And finally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 728478.0,
      "end_time": 732468.0,
      "text": "believe in your abilities and your creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 733270.0,
      "end_time": 736372.0,
      "text": "because you can do it yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 737259.0,
      "end_time": 738413.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 738437.0,
      "end_time": 744915.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}